launchbrowser() - Method in class com.project.testbase.TestBase
This method 'launchbrowser' is used to launch browser as per the mentioned browser in config.properties Browser support - chrome, firefox, ie There are option exposed in config.properties file for Chrome browser like: requireIncognito(set as Y) - If you want to launch the browser in incognito, requireHeadless(set as Y) - If you want to launch the browser in headless mode, existingBrowserWindow(set as Y) - If you want to execute test case in existing browser.
